{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "金逐流与史红英失散后独自来到济南大明湖游览，在历下亭遇到卖艺父女何老大与何凤，遭恶霸曹家的教头和打手骚扰。何凤以鼓锤击退教头，但曹公子带两名高手连城虎、彭巨峰前来强抢。红缨会香主宫秉藩仗义出手对抗曹家恶霸，与连城虎激战数十招。金逐流在旁观战后挺身而出，先以玄铁匣子硬碰彭巨峰的大力金刚掌致其双臂骨折，再以指代笔施展连家惊神笔法，空手夺笔完成“四笔点八脉”绝技击败连城虎，救下何家父女。宫秉藩对金逐流的武功刮目相看。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻薄少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到乌鸦也能养出了凤凰。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢列位看官捧场，我叫这丫头孝敬列位两段鼓书，唱得不好，请大家包涵。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻薄少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "美人儿唱的曲子，不用说，那一定是好的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若然列位看官认为还过得去，那就请大家随便赏赐赏赐。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "恶奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，唱得真好！你不必在这里讨钱了，五文十文的没有什么意思，带了你的闺女，到我们府中，向公子爷讨赏吧。公子爷一欢喜，包你一生吃喝不尽。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和你们的公子爷素不相识，不敢踵府领赏。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "教头",
      "listener": "char_he_lao_da",
      "text": "你们去了，不就认识了。嘿，嘿，你不认识我们的公子爷，我们的公子爷可早就认识你的闺女了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮腔者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿，嘿，张家的公子爷看上了你的闺女，你可是天大的造化到啦！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "教头",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "好小子，你要和我家的公子爷比拼有钱怎么着？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_jiao_tou",
      "text": "不敢，我只是个穷小子，岂敢狗眼看人低呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_tou",
      "text": "我跟你回去拜见你的公子爷就是，你可不能迁怒旁人呀！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "教头",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "好，有这位姑娘说情，便宜了你这小子，走吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_tou",
      "text": "我最恨狗杖人势的奴才，你既然定要逞凶，不给你一点厉害瞧瞧，你也不知我的本领。去吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "凤丫头，你闯了大祸了，快走，快走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_he_lao_da",
      "text": "大不了不过得罪一个土豪恶霸，怕他什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "唉，你这野丫头简直是不知天高地厚，那些人是不能招惹的，他们的好手还未来呢。你把金子还给这位相公，自们快走。再迟些就来不及。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "多谢相公厚赐，愚父女心领了，请相公也快走吧，免得受了牵累。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "小可仰慕姑娘色艺双绝，特遣家人前来邀请，请姑娘移玉寒舍，小可得以稍尽地主之谊，不料这些奴才不会说话，得罪了姑娘。小可这厢赔罪了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "我们父女是在江湖上卖艺混饭吃的，但却还不至于那样下贱，要去奉承富贵人家，登门侑酒。你硬来也好，软来也好，我就是不去！你给我滚开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "姑娘言重了，小可是专诚来请姑娘的，岂敢把你当作下贱的艺人！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "你的话说完了没有，休再罗咳，我可没有工夫与你瞎扯朗缠！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "姑娘这么不给面子？对不住，你不去也得去了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子，小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "凤儿小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "不必担心，这个雌儿不是咱们公子爷的对手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "姑娘，我劝你休要敬酒不吃吃罚洒，还是跟我走吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "天下有这样横蛮霸道的请客的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "我不把你这丫头抓到我的手中，难解我心头之恨！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "好呀，你们擅会倚势凌人，我斩你的狗爪子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "小娘子，你这话可是说得不对了。我们一个打你们一个，怎能说是倚势凌人？哈哈，我还是空手斗你的刀呢！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "彭寨主，今日怎么有这样好的兴致和人打架？为的是什么事情，可以说给兄弟听听么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "宫香主，什么风把你吹到这儿来了？你歇一会儿，兄弟就来陪你说话。",
      "tone": "尴尬",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "你知道我的性子急？这个闷葫芦没打开，我可是歇不下来的呵！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "宫香主，我劝你莫管闹事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "原来连寨主也在这儿，真是幸会了。怎么，这个事是管不得的吗？但究竟是怎么一回事情，你也该让我知道啊！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "我说管不得就管不得！你想要知道，这个架打完了，我陪你喝酒去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "喝酒不急，眼前的事可是等不得的，等你们这一架打完，人家的小姑娘可就要吃了大亏啦！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "宫香主，你究竟是想要怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "哼，你们不说，我就不知道吗？不过，我要你们自己说。你说，这两位说书的父女究竟有什么地方得罪了你？说出来让我评评理，否则……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "否则怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "否则这个闲事我宫某是管定的了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "什么东西，也配来管你家公子的事？连师父，把他拿下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子有所不知，这位宫先生是红缨会的香主，嘿，嘿，都是一条线上的朋友！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "什么线上的朋友，我可高攀不起！嘿，嘿，听说你们两位大寨主做了曹家的保缥，功名富贵，是指日可待了哪！这位想必就是曹公子吧？威风好大啊！连寨主，公子爷有令了，你上来拿我啊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "曹公子",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "红缨会是什么东西，小小一个江湖上的帮会就能吓倒了我？好呀，你敢在我的面前放肆，我先要了你的脑袋！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "不必公子爷劳神，你要我的脑袋是吗？我奉送就是！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_cao_gong_zi",
      "text": "公子，不可！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们曹家的老祖宗曹孟德割发代首，我如今效法你家的老祖宗，以帽代首，可惜你这位公子爷却要不了我的假脑袋！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "姓宫的，我只是看在红缨会的份上，不想与你抓破面子，你以为我当真怕了你么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "好呀，那么咱们把话先说明了。今日之事与红缨会无关，只是我宫某路见不平，要找你的晦气，你怎么样？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "宫秉藩，你，你欺人太甚！好呀，那咱们就比划比划，谁也不必牵连任何一方！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "speaker_name": "宫秉藩",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_he_lao_da",
      "text": "爹，你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "没什么。凤儿，你快走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": "char_he_lao_da",
      "text": "爹爹，你呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_he_feng",
      "text": "傻丫头，爹爹哪有走的道理？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，要死咱们父女也死在一起！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_he_lao_da",
      "text": "你们活得不耐烦了，赶着去见阎王么？别忙，别忙，等会儿我自会招呼你们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "你这小子在这里笑什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "第一个笑你！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "我有什么给你笑的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "可笑你这四笔点八脉的笔法只使得出一半，却尾然敢在这里逞能！唉，连家人才凋谢，可叹，可叹！",
      "tone": "嘲笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "我就是只使得出一半，你也破解不了，不信你来试试。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "别忙，别忙，待我笑够了再说。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "你还要笑谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "第二个就是笑你了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "你又笑我什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "笑你的金刚掌火候太差，只能称做泥菩萨掌。少林寺出了你这样的弟子，达摩祖师的面子也给你丢光了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "好，你说我的金刚掌不济事，你就来试试！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "你不信么？这就来了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "小心了，这东西是不能碰的！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "如何？我说你是泥菩萨掌你不相信，你看，如今是不是自身难保了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "你这小子弄奸，匣子里装的什么东西，叫我上当？哼，你有本领，你敢与我硬拼一掌么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "我早就提醒过你的，谁叫你碰我的匣子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "闲话少说，你敢不敢与我见个真章？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "有何不敢？看掌！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "speaker_name": "彭巨峰",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "如何？见了真章，你还不是一样的自身难保？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_peng_ju_feng",
      "text": "你放心好好的治理你自己吧，我是一向不打落水狗的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_gong_bing_fan",
      "text": "现在轮到你这个矮子啦！宫大哥，让我一让。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "你说过要破我这惊神笔法的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "何老大",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "人家手里没有判官笔，你管得着人家如何打法？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "不怕，不怕。我没有判官笔一样可以使出四笔点八脉的功夫。我说过的话就算数，一定要叫这矮子输得心服口服！",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "好，你就破吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "不错，你的本领的确是在我之上，但你使的却也还不是四笔点八脉的功夫！你若是要打败我，我现在就可以拱手认输。若要我输得心服口服，那你还得再显本领！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫吵，莫吵！我说过的话，当然算数！",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "四笔点八脉的功夫来啦。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "你服了么？我不想你的连家笔法失传，今日权且放过了你！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    }
